    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>In my case fix was to update <code>Run/Debug Configurations</code> and select in <code>Shorten command line</code> the next option <code>classpath file</code>.\n<a href=\"https://i.sstatic.net/tgCuu.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://i.sstatic.net/tgCuu.png\" alt=\"enter image description here\" /></a></p>\n"
