    "question_id" : 6381213,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>Did this on Intelij community 2021.1 windows, Worked fine :)</p>\n<ol>\n<li>On the edit configuration menu, click on modify options</li>\n</ol>\n<hr />\n<ol start=\"2\">\n<li>And then select Shorten command line</li>\n</ol>\n<hr />\n<ol start=\"3\">\n<li>Select JAR manifest option, apply &amp; run</li>\n</ol>\n<p><a href=\"https://i.sstatic.net/lvsif.png\" rel=\"noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://i.sstatic.net/lvsif.png\" alt=\"enter image description here\" /></a></p>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 3965515,
      "reputation" : 2670,
      "user_id" : 3271600,
      "user_type" : "registered",
      "accept_rate" : 27,
      "profile_image" : "https://i.sstatic.net/Jp5D8.png?s=256",
      "display_name" : "GvSharma",
