    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>This solved the problem for me on - <strong>IntelliJ Idea version - 2022.2.3 (ultimate edition)</strong></p>\n<p>Run &gt; Edit Configurations</p>\n<p>Modify Options &gt; Shorten command line</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://i.sstatic.net/mrk6c.png\" rel=\"noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://i.sstatic.net/mrk6c.png\" alt=\"enter image description here\" /></a></p>\n<p>Select JAR Manifest</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://i.sstatic.net/ROZme.png\" rel=\"noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://i.sstatic.net/ROZme.png\" alt=\"enter image description here\" /></a></p>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
